      desc 'server for a multi-player graphical multi user dungeon combat type game
crossfire is a multi-player graphical
arcade and adventure game made for X.
It has certain flavours from other games,
especially Gauntlet and the rogue-like
games (Nethack, Moria, Angband, and Ragnarok).
Any number of players can move around in their own window, 
finding and using items and battling monsters.
They can choose to cooperate or compete in the same world.'

